Steps:
=============

1. Get a domain.  $12/year
1.1 get a webhost $5/month

hostgator.com [ vendor]
After registering in hostgator, will get username, domain, server ip.

2. Upload your files
Using cyberduck, upload your files to the server ip given by hostgator using FTP.
Paste all your files under www folder.
Any change in the code, test locally and move the updated code to the server.


3. Website is live.
